fields.physical_description:
1.  box; tin enamelled mid blue with the title JUNEERO printed in large red and black letters on the front below the clasp; inside the lid which is hinged is pasted a paper label which gives the title and list of contents
2.  The Juneero Instruction Manual, by J Harrison, price 6d.; 64 page soft cover book giving details and instructions 
3.  leaflet, Juneero Materials and Accessories, pale green paper with black printing
4.  leaflet, You Can Make Scrolls, curves and Circles, pink paper with black printing
5.  Juneero Design No.10, Excavator, price 4d; double sided white with blue printing
6.  Juneero Design sheet, No.51, Air Raid Shelter, price 1d; white sheet with black printing
7.  Juneero Design sheet, No.52, Rocker Blotter, price 1d; white sheet with black printing
8.  Juneero Design sheet, No.59, Black Out Lantern, price 1d; blue sheet with black printing
9.  Juneero Design sheet, No.61, Engine Shed, price 1d; blue sheet with black printing 
10. Juneero Design sheet, No.63, French Tank, price 1d; blue sheet with black printing
11. Juneero Design sheet, No.65, Transmitting Station, price 1d; blue sheet with black printing
12.  Juneero Design sheet, No.66, Tapper, price 1d; blue sheet with black printing
13.  Juneero Design sheet, No.82, Juneero Engraving Machine price 1d; white sheet with black printing
14.  box lining, brown corrugated card
15.  patent multipurpose tool, metal mounted on wood painted blue; the remains of the Juneero label is on one end
